sorcer.core.provider

Class ControlFlowManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • sorcer.core.provider.ControlFlowManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MonitoringControlFlowManager

    public class ControlFlowManager
extends Object
    The ControlFlowManager class is responsible for handling control flow exertions (Conditional, NetJob, NetTask). This class is used by the ExertionDispatcher class for executing Exertions.
    Author:
    Mike Sobolewski
